{"tid":1367496,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【入元朗食嘢朋友必睇】","createTime":"2019-07-26T09:27:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T10:09:20.000Z","uid":261435,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"0a8d8e041edae230f80389d12ce8877756ea858b","tid":1367496,"uid":261435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T09:27:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <strong>香城online expansion pack: 外掛裝甲+Backpack 盾</strong> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">長文！如果巴絲趕時間就跳到啲圖到喇 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span> <br />\n<br />\n最近香城online嘅開發可謂如火如荼，expansion pack 不停出現，但主要升級都集中咗係怪物嗰面，啲怪物用橡皮彈呀，催喊彈呀越來越無限制。然後又多咗新嘅怪物角色，popo犬之外，又加埋白衫怪，裝甲值唔高啫，但野野都無差別攻擊，好犯規囉。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n咁一面倒嘅設計，對人類角色嘅玩家實在太唔公平！所以我覺得下一步開發，要集中返所有人類玩家都用到嘅升級package。而我有個提議，就係加強玩家嘅防護力，咁先公平嘛 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n <br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">我個提議叫：通用複合外掛裝甲 <br />\n主要用於升級防護道具，例如盾、多用途背包、甚至衣裝。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong><br />\n <br />\n望住香城online個設計就覺得好奇怪，點解每次升級，啲道具多數係完全唔同系列嘅呢？例如要升隻盾，就要由浮板盾一口氣轉到木盾，或者用現場嘅大型地盤盾，點解無一啲通用嘅升級方法嘅呢？我認為呢個係遊戲設計上嘅大敗筆。所以我認為可以循模組化通用升級方向發展，而我嘅設計概念，就係以下嘅外掛裝甲。（我animation真係唔得，所以下面會用實物去illustrate個概念）<br />\n <br />\n外掛裝甲嘅材料一定要係香城online本身已經好多嘅野，咁可以減低開發成本。<br />\n裝甲主要由四種材料組成<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">1)防穿透物料板（illustration 用𠝹板cutting board代表）<br />\n2)金屬片（illustration 用鐵尺代表）<br />\n3)雙面膠帶 （illustration 用雙面膠𥿄代表）<br />\n4)強力膠帶 （illustration 用強力封箱膠𥿄代表） </span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z58cHeW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ58cHeW.png&h=d8203a5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n做法可以多變，材料亦可以唔同，但先以A4 cutting board 做illustration <br />\n <br />\n玩家要先集齊<br />\n1)A4 防穿透物料板 x1<br />\n2) 大小適中金屬片 x1０<br />\n3)雙面膠帶 x 小量<br />\n4)強力膠帶 x 大量<br />\n <br />\n玩家此時要進入小遊戲模式進行合成<br />\n <br />\n首先，在防穿透物料板邊緣貼上雙面膠帶 ，用於確定鐵片安放位置；(如圖)<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z69Wptu.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ69Wptu.png&h=1d30d3b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n然後，面將鐵片逐塊攞起，然後用雙面膠帶完全固定 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XVdgptO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXVdgptO.png&h=6c1e920d&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/wkXpym9.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FwkXpym9.png&h=b71c3e48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n但此時鐵片一受衝擊就會剝落，所必須用強力膠帶徹底包起，完全固定。膠帶唔可以剪斷，要全條包。最好選用防水類，如果唔係落雨就會扣耐用值<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QPhH4t3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQPhH4t3.png&h=1e6da705&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PGUvtVL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPGUvtVL.png&h=fd419fb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n裝甲板就咁完成啦。<br />\n <br />\n但點附加呢？我其實想一眾巴打絲打集思廣益，各出奇謀，不拘一格咁做。但遊戲總需要個default setting。我提議兩種玩法<br />\n <br />\n1) 就咁用強力膠帶包上個盾度，缺點係樣衰，而且難以拆解換裝<br />\n2) 搜集追加道具(鑽+索帶)然後加工繫上 (如圖) <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/btrtZ2A.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbtrtZ2A.png&h=f291e3ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EYXEnfX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEYXEnfX.png&h=98daa502&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/b7gJOV8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fb7gJOV8.png&h=6f66f4c0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YuOTrHP.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYuOTrHP.png&h=4ee5c6d7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HvHAE2Q.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHvHAE2Q.png&h=80a32691&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n但講明係通用升級，咁就唔應該只用於現有嘅盾道具度啦，應該可以用來升級改做其他道具做防具先啱，例如多用途背包，可以透過搜集其他道具加工升級，成為有一定防護力嘅Backpack盾<br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">設想需要村料<br />\n１）已完成嘅外掛裝甲<br />\n２）cushion <br />\n３）大小適中背包<br />\n４）針線<br />\n５）皮革條，或強靭布料；針線（用蠟線會強靭啲架）<br />\n６）魔術貼</span><br />\n  <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Z2ESHgA.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZ2ESHgA.png&h=a3fee72b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zfAOfBC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzfAOfBC.png&h=db945c95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n完成品設想圖   <br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AxS8Z3s.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAxS8Z3s.png&h=567b5be8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/f1sEngO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Ff1sEngO.png&h=7589a2b5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yCUZ6Ju.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyCUZ6Ju.png&h=98754108&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n小遊戲內合成過程<br />\n <br />\n將兩條皮革縫在背包上，縫之前記得先度位 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，手嘅邊緣畫上線，縫到嗰個位就停。縫嘅時候，皮革要完全放平，唔使留位畀隻手穿入去，咁樣皮革同背包先可以緊貼手臂<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，唔緊貼，fing 下fing下 ，就會難以操控，要減防禦值，體力值消耗亦會較大<br />\n   <br />\n縫好之後就可以組裝啦，如果係有電腦格嘅背包會方便啲<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BuRmACm.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBuRmACm.png&h=b9a6b997&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DcBtZ34.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDcBtZ34.png&h=e9a1cdb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n  <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Gd3PKvz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGd3PKvz.png&h=0167a3bf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YOcg8Xi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYOcg8Xi.png&h=60aa6bf4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\nCushion 能夠吸走棍棒攻擊嘅大部分shock wave <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，而裝甲就可以抵擋棍棒打擊同埋刀劍攻擊。<br />\n <br />\n使用時記得將揹帶放到前面，用魔術貼固定，咁就唔會打到自己啦<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s0Jwdpr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs0Jwdpr.png&h=72c32ea4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBackpack 盾都有兩種握法，視乎你另一隻手係咪揸緊其他道具。<br />\n  <br />\n <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/LZh1ACV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FLZh1ACV.png&h=b22eac7a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/71G9Kwg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F71G9Kwg.png&h=03bdb617&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nBackpack 盾最大好處係可以將盾隱藏，唔會被popo犬一眼望到，就追住來咬，最啱唔打算上到最前線，又想增加防禦值嘅玩家。對抗白衫怪，應該猶其有效。<br />\n <br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">但上到最前嘅勇武玩家呢？</span>我諗可以將個外掛裝甲，附加落浮板盾、木盾、地盤盾度，以增加防護力；因為係模組化設計，只要搵到大啲嘅板、多啲長啲嘅鐵片，就可以加大個scale。而且可以考慮加入衣裝裏面，以增加對各種槍彈嘅防護力（雖然真係幫唔到打頭）。<br />\n <br />\n其實外掛裝甲只係一個概念，各玩家可以各色其色咁自行改裝。物料亦可以不拘一格。不過如果轉用其他物料，一定要做啲試驗，千祈唔好畀自己false sense of safety。無論如何，希望呢啲idea可以拋磚引玉，同大家一齊升級，唔好被啲怪物蝦啦。"},{"pid":"627ee6b6bfeaea571a7726ab117f0773f6619626","tid":1367496,"uid":25044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T09:29:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8d9841993c944ca21562014f007698c131882b39","tid":1367496,"uid":240425,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T09:31:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"85c41f5dd700173cbb1fd13dd5701f6a60132fd3","tid":1367496,"uid":100406,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T09:32:59.000Z","msg":"好難整喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a8926d30d5e2c2dec1c71dbda7c871cfcdcff67","tid":1367496,"uid":246026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T09:34:50.000Z","msg":"帶埋<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">[手鎚螺絲批手鋸平鉗</span></span><br />\n到時比班工程佬即場制造防具同武器"},{"pid":"4fc19e221d66763a94a9ca11e49084ba01545f44","tid":1367496,"uid":246026,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T09:35:49.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">更正</span></span><br />\n帶埋<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">[手鎚撞批手鋸平鉗</span></span><br />\n到時比班工程佬即場制造防具同武器"},{"pid":"c1b302c51e880ee072587405ce1c9a4d92dc6aba","tid":1367496,"uid":25045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T09:36:25.000Z","msg":"可以試下嘅"},{"pid":"b4c36593440bcb831cb111850d6cfeee3370240c","tid":1367496,"uid":246026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T09:39:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"06171709a6bc756684e62402fd4614eb258efac0","tid":1367496,"uid":246026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T09:41:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b34753462d529c656d792d9ad371db76a4954bc4","tid":1367496,"uid":246026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T09:44:55.000Z","msg":"請大家帶埋<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">手鎚撞批手鋸平鉗</span></span><br />\n到時比班工程佬即場制造防具同武器"},{"pid":"e9cf7b5c8638824e65e4108d45684a09c324eb86","tid":1367496,"uid":122988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T09:48:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cqxpyxg.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fcqxpyxg.jpg&h=850d78ef&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"acbdd2b2d6872debd0b29bb73cc995bce3c33dac","tid":1367496,"uid":138060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":